name: Unidentified_Wookiee_(Attichitcuk%27s_father%27s_victim)
content: A male Wookiee was killed in a duel by the father of Attichitcuk, who later emerged as a powerful Wookiee Chieftain. The death of that Wookiee caused a lasting enmity between his clan and that of Attichitcuk. Later, the grand-nephew of the deceased Wookiee met Chewbacca, son of Attichitcuk, and mentioned the vendetta between their two families.
